京都做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:16:24.000Z","msg":"其實我都好唔鐘意京都<br />\n京都無錯係好揼本，畫質好靚<br />\n但係次次都鐘意大改劇情<br />\n果種改唔係為左貼合動畫化既改<br />\n係覺得我寫得好過原作者果種改<br />\n十二集例牌要塞一集泳裝回一集聖誕節一集正月參拜<br />\n將前幾集用過既梗翻兜塞哂落去就做兩三集<br />\n<br />\n京都除左KAC我鐘意既係得日常<br />\n最燥底係佢龍女僕塞哂上面果d野落去都算<br />\n結局仲要改到不知所謂，完全同原作者想表達既野相反"},{"pid":"0991676757a752ae5d90bbae154004edc761665b","tid":2010234,"uid":186489,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6fc4e818a7d852d249fb1a0240b6598ad38d4126","tid":2010234,"uid":92201,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"a24ce09078d9cc2c3b25057b6d897f6ddbc26f52","tid":2010234,"uid":71885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T02:28:19.000Z","msg":"麻枝准仲有業界信用？"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T03:17:38.000Z","msg":"summer pocket<br />\n<br />\n到宜家為止, 我都覺得ab同charlotte係佳作"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"平心而論，Charlotte純粹無聊搵套番睇其實都ok既，起碼女主夠正先<br />\n但千祈唔好諗住當催淚神作咁睇<br />\n我已經係麻枝死忠，最盡都只可以比到咁既評價<br />\n<br />\nRewrite第一季就真係垃圾尼，第二季受第一季拖累亦唔會好得去邊<br />\n不過三首op三首ed都係佳作，唔睇片都應該聽下歌"},{"pid":"b07056bde8f34b6dc7eaa48718d48a708177ee89","tid":2010234,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9ecedf9c552d93b68907665fbc3ab43ece0ac545","tid":2010234,"uid":14733,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T10:18:26.000Z","msg":"麻枝准+PA work<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T05:29:58.000Z","msg":"神作（頭十集）"},{"pid":"c94a3c89a10b4507385dcf166520c28fb5a97473","tid":2010234,"uid":4493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"138c7ffa5f27c161f1354887566c67d37fe3afc2","tid":2010234,"uid":134174,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d61d5833051ad0ef1a6145c65029e95dbcbf